g startup, the worker applies the patch to each cached response before sending it back.","sentence_zh":"启动期间，Worker 会在返回响应前，把补丁应用到每个缓存响应上。","show_nodes":["before-sending-it-back"],"show_links":["before-sending-it-back->applies"],"focus_node":"before-sending-it-back","note_zh":"这一步说明补丁应用发生在响应返回之前。"}]}' WHERE id = 'apply-patch';
