h a simple default structure.","sentence_zh":"当开发者运行这个命令时，它会创建一个带有简单默认结构的新项目。","show_nodes":["when-a-developer-runs-the-command"],"show_links":["when-a-developer-runs-the-command->creates"],"focus_node":"when-a-developer-runs-the-command","note_zh":"这一步说明什么时候会创建项目。"}]}' WHERE id = 'create-project';
